{{advert|date=July 2018}} {{notability|date=July 2018}} {{infobox Organization |name = Horasis |image =Horasis_Logo_RGB.jpg |mission =Inspiring our future |formation = 2005 |type = [[think tank]] |location = [[Zurich]], [[Switzerland]] |region_served = Worldwide |leader_title = Chairman |leader_name = [[Frank-Jürgen Richter]] |website = {{URL|http://www.horasis.org/}} }}
'''Horasis''' is an independent [[think tank]] based in [[Zurich]], [[Switzerland]], which was established in 2005 by [[Frank-Jürgen Richter]], its chairman.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/fii-view/indian-companies-to-benefiteu-crisis-expert_566547.html |title=Indian companies to benefit from EU crisis: Expert - CNBC-TV18 |publisher=Moneycontrol.com |date=2011-07-19 |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref>
Horasis holds invitation-only meetings of global business leaders with a regional focus on [[China]], [[India]], and [[Southeast Asia]]. It has been dubbed "a kind of junior league World Economic Forum for the emerging market set" by [[The New York Times]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/09/world/asia/09iht-letter.html?pagewanted=all|author=Tom Redburn|title=Enthusiasm Temepered With Concern, About Business in India|newspaper=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=2013-11-02}}</ref> It also holds a Global Meeting, and hosts private events for the Horasis Visionary Circle, a peer-to-peer group of entrepreneurs. ==Activities== Horasis provides a platform for cooperation and knowledge-sharing, particularly between developed countries and emerging markets.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businesstoday.co.om/disCon.aspx?Cval=908 |title=Article: Emerging markets to the fore |publisher=Businesstoday.co.om |date= |accessdate=2013-07-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314210959/http://www.businesstoday.co.om/disCon.aspx?Cval=908|archivedate=2012-03-14}}</ref> The community works principally through partnerships with corporations, governments and international organizations, often serving as an incubator for new initiatives.These meetings rotate amongst host countries which stage the events;<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcit.gov.cy/mcit/mcit.nsf/0/69FAA238A35E51B4C225787000247859?OpenDocument |title=Ministry of Commerce, Industry and Tourism - Archived Speeches/Articles/Interviews - Global Russia Business Meeting, address by Minister of Commerce |publisher=Mcit.gov.cy |date=2011-04-11 |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref> selected corporations supplement speeches and presentations about actual topics.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bankofcyprus.com.cy/en-GB/Cyprus/News-Archive/The-Bank-of-Cyprus-at-the-Global-Russia-Business-Meeting/ |title=The Bank of Cyprus at the Global Russia Business Meeting - Bank of Cyprus Country Cyprus |publisher=Bankofcyprus.com.cy |date=2011-04-18 |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pwc.com/lu/en/china/global-china-business-meeting.jhtml |title=Global China Business Meeting by PwC PwC Luxembourg |publisher=Pwc.com |date=2010-11-22 |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref>
Horasis meetings are usually held in a host country outside the geographic location of the 'in-focus' nation. The events are a means for the countries 'in focus' as guests (China, India, and South East Asia) to promote relations with the world and to display [[soft power]] through co-option and cooperation. The meetings are also a platform for the host country to engage in policy dialogue with the guest countries.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gouvernement.lu/salle_presse/discours/premier_ministre/2010/11-novembre/22-juncker/index.html |title=Jean-Claude Juncker, Discours à l'occasion du Global China Business Meeting, Luxembourg |publisher=Gouvernement.lu |date=2010-11-22 |accessdate=2013-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323003412/http://www.gouvernement.lu/salle_presse/discours/premier_ministre/2010/11-novembre/22-juncker/index.html |archivedate=2012-03-23 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metricstream.com/pressNews/pr_307_horasis_summit_italy_gunjan_sinha.html |title=Gunjan Sinha to participate in the Horasis Summit in Naples, Italy – Press Release |publisher=Metricstream.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref> == Global Meeting == The annual Horasis Global Meeting is a gathering of business people with government officials, scientists and intellectuals. Around 500 participants from 70 countries gather every year to discuss issues concerning corporations and societies. The 2016 meeting was held in [[Liverpool|Liverpool;]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Global leaders arrive in Liverpool for the International Festival for Business 2016|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/news/business/global-leaders-arrive-liverpool-international-11455234|website=Liverpool Echo|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Big names descending on Liverpool for IFB2016|url=https://www.insidermedia.com/insider/national/big-names-descending-on-liverpool-for-ifb2016|website=Insider Media Ltd|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref> the 2017 Horasis at the Portuguese seaside resort of [[Cascais]]. Issues such as economic growth, innovation, migration and inequality usually figure in the debates.<ref>{{cite web|title=Investimento. 200 mil milhões à caçaem Lisboa|url=https://www.dinheirovivo.pt/economia/investimento-200-mil-milhoes-a-caca-em-lisboa/|website=Dinheiro Vivo|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rota do futuro global passapor Cascais|url=https://sol.sapo.pt/artigo/565345/rota-do-futuro-global-passa-por-cascais-|website=Jornal SOL|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref>
== Regional Meetings == Horasis holds the Horasis China Meeting, the Horasis India Meeting and the Horasis Asia Meeting on an annual basis.<ref>{{cite web|title=Forum participants confident about future of Chinese economy|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2017-11/08/c_136735048.htm|website=Xinhua News Agency|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref> In 2017, the Horasis China Meeting was for the first time held in [[Sheffield]], UK, and was attended by more than 300 Chinese business people, including representatives from state-owned companies, investment funds and private firms, as well as their British counterparts.<ref>{{cite web|title=Chinese wowed by Sheffield’s huge potential|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/business/chinese-wowed-by-sheffield-s-huge-potential-1-8843414|website=The Star|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref> The international Horasis India Meeting is attended by hundreds of business people and politicians from India and around the world.<ref>{{cite web|title=Speech by Minister of State of External Affairs on "Portugal and India - Forging a New Growth Partnership" at the Horasis India Meeting, Cascais (July 03, 2016)|url=http://mea.gov.in/Speeches-Statements.htm?dtl/26983/Speech+by+Minister+of+State+of+External+Affairs+on+Portugal+and+India++Forging+a+New+Growth+Partnership+at+the+Horasis+India+Meeting+Cascais+July+03+2016|website=Ministry of External Affairs, Government of India|accessdate=19 November 2017}}</ref> The Horasis Asia Meeting in 2017 was co-hosted by the [[Government of West Bengal]] and the Indian Chamber of Commerce (ICC).<ref>{{cite web|title=Mandalay Chief Minister calls for foreign investment in India meet|url=http://www.mizzima.com/business-domestic/mandalay-chief-minister-calls-foreign-investment-india-meet|website=Mizzima|accessdate=27 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Digital India: 'Digital companies taking control over global economy a concern'|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/company/corporate-trends/digital-companies-taking-control-over-global-economy-a-concern/articleshow/61810493.cms|website=The Economic Times|accessdate=27 November 2017}}</ref>
==Business Leaders of the Year== Horasis awards the "Business Leaders of the Year" award for entrepreneurs who have been building and leading successful global firms. The award was first given in 2006.<ref>{{cite web|author=Horasis.org |url=http://www.horasis.org/press_releases_all_27.php |title=News :: Business Leader of the Year |publisher=Horasis.org |date= |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref> The award ceremonies take place at the regional meetings.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.benzinga.com/press-releases/10/09/b494889/roland-berger-strategy-consultants-and-horasis-award-arab-business-lead#ixzz1WJRYRJ7O |title=Roland Berger Strategy Consultants and Horasis Award "Arab Business Leaders of the Year 2010" |publisher=Benzinga |date=2010-09-27 |accessdate=2013-07-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.horasis.org/Horasis%20Global%20China%20Business%20Meeting%202011%20-%20report.pdf |title=Horasis :Global China Business Meeting |publisher=Horasis.org |accessdate=2013-11-02}}</ref>
