{{EngvarB|date=October 2017}}
{{Infobox operational plan
| name        = Operation Cycle
| partof      = the [[Battle of France]]
| image       = File:4June-12June Battle of France.PNG
|image_size = 300px
| caption     = The German offensive to the [[Seine]], 4–12 June 1940.
| type        = Evacuation
| location    = Le Havre
| coordinates = {{Coord|49|29|N|00|06|E|type:event_region:FR|display=inline,title}}
| date        = 10–13 June 1940
| objective   = Withdrawal
| executed_by = [[Royal Navy]]<br />[[French Navy]]<br />Allied naval vessels
| outcome     = Allied success
| casualties  =
